Class ExperimentManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.rocketapp.controller.ExperimentManager
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MockExperimentManager

    public class ExperimentManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that handles adding, retrieving, and modifying experiments from firestore. Singleton with static methods for convenience.

      • listen

        public static void listen(Experiment experiment,
                          ObjectCallback<Experiment> onUpdate)
        Listens to firestore for changes to this experiment. You MUST use this to get the trials and questions for an experiment. You may want to update the UI in onUpdate.
        Parameters:
        experiment - The experiment to listen to.
        onUpdate - Callback for implementing desired behaviour when the experiment is updated in firestore.
